# Sensitive File Rules

Apply extra caution in these files:

- `app/p/[slug]/**`: keep server-rendered behavior intact.
- `lib/claude.js`: this is the only Claude integration entrypoint.
- `middleware.js`: auth flow is protected; change only on explicit request.
- `models/**/*.js`: schema changes require explicit confirmation.

If asked to change these areas, verify requirement intent before editing.
